        "description": "<p><a href=\"https://fondy.io/gb/plugins/paid-memberships-pro/?utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_medium=cms\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">This Paid memberships Pro payment plugin</a> adds Fondy as payment gateway to plugin Paid memberships Pro. Fondy can accept VISA and MasterCard securely, quickly and easily on your store in minutes. Recurring payments, simple, straightforward pricing, top notch fraud intelligence, and 24/7 support.</p>\n<h4>Start with Fondy</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://portal.fondy.eu/mportal/#/account/registration?utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_medium=cms\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Create Free Fondy Account</a></p>\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Customize your checkout window (<a href=\"http://jsfiddle.net/8h65h91t/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Some styles</a>)</li>\n<li>Easy configuration &#8211; only Merchant ID and Secret Key!</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Allowed currencies</h3>\n<p>With us your customers can make purchases in many currencies. Fondy support  EUR, USD, GBP, UAH and some other.</p>\n<h3>Tariffs</h3>\n<p>Only commission with payment. It is possible to adjust payment of the commission on itself, or to impose on the client.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fondy.io/gb/pricing/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">See current tariffs on the Fondy website</a></p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Ensure you have latest version of plugin installed (Paid memberships Pro)</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin files to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code>(or upload the plugin zip file using wp-admin.)</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "<p>Some answers you can find here <a href=\"https://fondy.io/en/faq/?utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_medium=cms\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a></p>\n",
